{"tid":1458044,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【分析】睇戲都知，對家行動一定有plan a plan b，要知要學","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:45:52.000Z","uid":157304,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5f2c825ba7725afc1afd33aef866bdac1c69beac","tid":1458044,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"好似今日咁，面對幾十萬人入機場咁大單嘢，對家好明顯開晒會有plan a plan b應對，甚至c d e<br />\n<br />\n暫時睇嚟：<br />\nPlan a：散播流言會圍捕，宣布停飛，等人自己散，夜晚再喺各車站捉少數夜走嘅手足，繼續散播白色恐怖，復飛，引發分化互屌（上策，不戰屈人兵）<br />\n<br />\nPlan b ：大家唔散，就會等到最後一班機嘅搭客散咗就會block網絡同大部份去路，喺機場呢個死地驅散同圍捕抗爭者，走得快嘅趕走，走得慢嘅拉，話我哋非法集會乜乜柒（中策，行動有變數，而且可能民怨再加劇）<br />\n<br />\nPlan c：最低機會發生，大致同上，但面對解勇武還手，或者可能叫扮示威者嘅差佬衝擊禁區之類，再用極高武力鎮壓同驅散，定性今日係恐襲之類（下策，半攬炒，有排拆所以幾乎唔會發生，但一定已有呢個準備）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003f19e3f1efa9f20a60e6fef7a4d2264d1c4b83","tid":1458044,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c2dd6e6617d7e121e47a526341e679ecd6852733","tid":1458044,"uid":280436,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"【散 定唔散 都係政府個局入面】<br />\n<br />\n政府<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">操縱緊我地嘅言論</span></span>去<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">分化</span></span>勇武同和理非<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果散</span> <br />\n就發表大量<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌撚散水狗</span></span></span>嘅言論<br />\n馬後砲<br />\n指責班合理擔心安全嘅和理非<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">be water</span></span>係大家一直以來重視嘅嘢<br />\n根本勇武唔會怪責<br />\n可見係政府故意引起割席<br />\n<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\">唔散</span><br />\n警察真係做嘢<br />\n就會湧現和理非怪責勇武嘅言論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一切 都係政府設下嘅套路！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日真係有取消/延誤航班 <br />\n警察真係有佈防 而且有機會用得到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但真正目的並非實質行動<br />\n而係分化大家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最近安插臥底係前線同樣<br />\n都有一層目的係為左令尼場運動嘅參與者<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自行瓦解</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大量網軍混入連登，Facebook，telegram<br />\n散播謠言<br />\n令大家<span style=\"color: red;\">質疑</span>盟友嘅可信性<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">互相猜忌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家千奇唔好中政府嘅詭計</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">謹記 不分化 不割席</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢嘅陰濕招數 我地只要團結 一定搵到方法破解"},{"pid":"38d2c89b701177712b3c200763646f71a4659498","tid":1458044,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ff06d5c809ce8907e120284d654101e657e85a5d","tid":1458044,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:58:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ac7083e50919605b2d34c4d59d0c89212d989e57","tid":1458044,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:59:42.000Z","msg":"Sorry ching 借位<br />\n<br />\n突發！ 816攬炒啦你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f59c51cafe8becca33e70f5bb5361bab74967417","tid":1458044,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"5be0a88aad91a615d5630b9ad5a656f187df2ded","tid":1458044,"uid":125470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef2032e2ff62fade6f4b490536b7fc3c79b2f97","tid":1458044,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:04:44.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n最重要係唔好互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae54eae5beff81fd6437c4d68020d8eed74c3e2c","tid":1458044,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"留緊係機場 唔覺得會好似你所講咁會清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd1814f6a60c599c4c9b32ae12ec8af1535927e","tid":1458044,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"咩叫奇兵對正兵，正兵對奇兵?"},{"pid":"2b35fc079498fcd570cc08b8ad05a3bc0b65a165","tid":1458044,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc1a8a6f4dd3462b2c9450638c60a7a7e7d79e5","tid":1458044,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0cdfb35c87950cb337d81d80687e8af0323d142","tid":1458044,"uid":157304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae54eae5beff81fd6437c4d68020d8eed74c3e2c","tid":1458044,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"留緊係機場 唔覺得會好似你所講咁會清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:12:59.000Z","msg":"而家已經完成咗plan a，唔會清了<br />\nPlan b唔散可能會清"},{"pid":"597ccb0f2687c4d4f845ebba7d1d995e10bf0728","tid":1458044,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd1814f6a60c599c4c9b32ae12ec8af1535927e","tid":1458044,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"咩叫奇兵對正兵，正兵對奇兵?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"可以睇孫子兵法，有語譯版<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/sheracaolity/%E5%AD%AB%E5%AD%90%E5%85%B5%E6%B3%95-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80-1ec6ec9984c7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fsheracaolity%2F%25E5%25AD%25AB%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2585%25B5%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25AE%2580-1ec6ec9984c7&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=a3bce6d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/sheracaolity/%E5%AD%AB%E5%AD%90%E5%85%B5%E6%B3%95-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80-1ec6ec9984c7</a>"},{"pid":"1f05eebe8fffb8d477609342877be050afc609ed","tid":1458044,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:26:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"4d4221ff28be06d3da5010b7ea7390df5b5c06f5","tid":1458044,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2572c709c51dd4fc8d7145ae48f63a1f0d2612","tid":1458044,"uid":65522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:46:04.000Z","msg":"所以其實前線判斷先係最正確，上唔到網既情況下我地又唔知現場點現場又報唔到料"},{"pid":"5df3aa9a02736502b228be14662962578a0b142f","tid":1458044,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd1814f6a60c599c4c9b32ae12ec8af1535927e","tid":1458044,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"咩叫奇兵對正兵，正兵對奇兵?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"我都唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d95edcff45f19d383b0d949c3dc4156051b7031","tid":1458044,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:58:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75cf30eea3c64eb1b6f401d5339eeea0eec7e622","tid":1458044,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:17:52.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"580b118b7011355ab9e415e57689aa0bb2ff087b","tid":1458044,"uid":157304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5df3aa9a02736502b228be14662962578a0b142f","tid":1458044,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd1814f6a60c599c4c9b32ae12ec8af1535927e","tid":1458044,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"咩叫奇兵對正兵，正兵對奇兵?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"我都唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"一般的作戰，總是以「正兵」合戰，用「奇兵」取勝。出奇才能制勝 <br />\n講白一點 <br />\n一般的作戰原則，通常不是靠正面廝殺取勝的，而是靠巧妙的戰術運用，或是特殊的戰法來智取 <br />\n<br />\n孫子在兵法理論中，提出一個「奇正」的命題， <br />\n「出奇制勝」體現了孫子合理部署兵力、靈活運用戰術的思想，作為一般的作戰原則。 <br />\n<br />\n「明於正，暗於奇」 <br />\n與敵正面作戰為正，圍剿、包抄為奇;列陣對敵、明攻為正，突擊、偷襲或採用特殊戰法為奇 <br />\n作戰必須有「正奇」的變化，要「以正合，以奇勝」才能戰勝敵人。 <br />\n<br />\n企業界常說「人無我有，人有我優，人優我多，人多我轉。」 其核心就是「出奇制勝」。 <br />\n在競爭激烈的商業戰場上求生存與發展，最忌諱的就是步人後塵。 <br />\n齊白石曾經說:「像我者死!」這正是在告誡他人，不要仿效，要不斷的創新"},{"pid":"c21d63db886708a77587be29374d43dfa01e6ff1","tid":1458044,"uid":157304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5df3aa9a02736502b228be14662962578a0b142f","tid":1458044,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd1814f6a60c599c4c9b32ae12ec8af1535927e","tid":1458044,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"咩叫奇兵對正兵，正兵對奇兵?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"我都唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:25:49.000Z","msg":"在戰術上，孫子的核心戰術是「以正合，以奇勝」。簡單來講就是分兵的策略：正在打的是正兵，留在手中留給之後打的是奇兵。就好像紅、綠、藍三原色可以調出任何其他顏色一樣，正、奇的觀念簡單，但混合起來可以設計的戰術變化無窮。<br />\n以韓信破趙的戰役為例，韓信晚上派兩千兵力預備，清晨放一萬兵力背水列陣，自己再帶一支部隊出去迎戰，一共是一正二奇。大戰良久，韓信假裝敗退，扔下大將旗鼓，退回水邊和一萬兵力會和，變成一正一奇。背水列陣的漢軍被置之死地、無退路，因此全都拼了全力在打，這是韓信造的「死地之勢」，可引出部隊的最大戰力；而趙軍以為自己佔優、要決一死戰了，便動員全部兵力，連同待在軍營的預備隊一齊出動，一下子便只有正兵，沒有奇兵。韓信預備的兩千奇兵一見到機會出現，就直搗趙軍軍營，拔趙旗插漢旗，瞬間奪下敵營，逼得趙軍回師奪營。此時兩千奇兵與趙軍交鋒，故轉變成正兵；韓信背水列陣的兵力則成了奇兵。趙軍當下有正無奇，向前又入不了營，軍心亂了，韓信的一萬奇兵馬上轉為正兵，從背後掩殺而來，兩面夾擊滅了趙軍。<br />\n韓信破趙，整體經歷三次正奇轉換，而在每個局部上則發生無數次正奇轉換。戰鬥中時時刻刻是正奇轉換，用足球來比喻的話，當你接到球時，你就是正；而當你在無球跑位時，則是奇。球場上每分每秒亦是正奇的轉換，勝機一出現，馬上派出奇兵、射門、得分。因此善用正奇者勝。當然，要能善用正奇，大前提還是士兵體能要有、技術要有、經驗要有，組織的管理要有、指揮系統要有，將軍的領導力要有、戰術規劃的能力要有。這些全有了，戰術正確、執行力也高，奪勝自如探囊取物。"},{"pid":"bf4ad790fd941999fb6c8735ab876ec2469ca303","tid":1458044,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:38:36.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"d3eac2f00f70d549ee6d2f5d6ccbaaa2d6da3329","tid":1458044,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c70426190d4277cb951a379a3f26db6bcff8fc7","tid":1458044,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e0f5642522148bc20bcf6b9527fc224c813b01","tid":1458044,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"認真主線文<br />\n求讀者"},{"pid":"67ae55f34eb1483d9ba88683e40d68ae32fb722b","tid":1458044,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:46:33.000Z","msg":"小心「狼來了」<br />\n講一百次大話等我地鬆懈，再一舉殲滅"},{"pid":"39e46d082b763c445edb65b98a489633fc1cccde","tid":1458044,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:49:34.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得太多post太亂？我整左個策略、行動、文宣方向精華集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFUfDD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFUfDD.png&h=51ddb9e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">機場檢討POST懶人包</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1</a><br />\n我係空管主任，我想講今日機場真係呢兩個幾月黎香港人贏得最靚既一仗<br />\n<br />\n<a 