常不是靠正面廝殺取勝的，而是靠巧妙的戰術運用，或是特殊的戰法來智取 <br />\n<br />\n孫子在兵法理論中，提出一個「奇正」的命題， <br />\n「出奇制勝」體現了孫子合理部署兵力、靈活運用戰術的思想，作為一般的作戰原則。 <br />\n<br />\n「明於正，暗於奇」 <br />\n與敵正面作戰為正，圍剿、包抄為奇;列陣對敵、明攻為正，突擊、偷襲或採用特殊戰法為奇 <br />\n作戰必須有「正奇」的變化，要「以正合，以奇勝」才能戰勝敵人。 <br />\n<br />\n企業界常說「人無我有，人有我優，人優我多，人多我轉。」 其核心就是「出奇制勝」。 <br />\n在競爭激烈的商業戰場上求生存與發展，最忌諱的就是步人後塵。 <br />\n齊白石曾經說:「像我者死!」這正是在告誡他人，不要仿效，要不斷的創新"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22823e89bbfd638be6c41a7e99d3affddbbe66fc","tid":1458044,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25de0cf43516a592b17da9d95951faabed21c2e","tid":1458044,"uid":282591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:05:50.000Z","msg":"三個plan都好正路，如果係昨天出，可信性大D，今晚出就有D事後....<br />\nanyway啦，今日全日係現場，D風亂咁吹，解畫解到手軟，講到尾信前線啦。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"4b5134dd14dfce49759df11f53b38ba1fe12d7f9","tid":1458044,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:09:35.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f92a48818c63dd428e950c02b489f6fc1350d5de","tid":1458044,"uid":4948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U5kpCHq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5kpCHq.png&h=4602514d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fe399df9a6cbd3a9586055151c3d9277c38f553","tid":1458044,"uid":4948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U5kpCHq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU5kpCHq.png&h=4602514d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88b1173314272ef10d29d2c8412429d0c9ee18f1","tid":1458044,"uid":4948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0